SOURCE

https://www.engadget.com/2017/05/04/neural-networks-can-help-animate-video-games/

AGENT

Research at University of Edinburgh

GOAL

To automatically create animations based on a characters state, geometry of the scene and user input

DATA

Animations and sprites from a large collection of games

METHODS

Neural networks

RESULTS

Results can be seen here:
